title: What can I do if I cannot access the terminal configuration page?
answer:
1. Ensure that the power supply of the terminal works properly and that the network cables of the terminal are properly connected.
2. Check the IP address of your computer and ensure that this IP address is in the same network segment as the LAN IP address of the terminal.
3. Ensure that your Web browser does not use a proxy server.
4. Ensure that you have entered the correct user name and user password that are used for accessing the terminal configuration page.
5. If the problem persists, restore the default settings of the terminal.
